  "short_description": "Sokowand is a top-down puzzle game which fuses sokoban-inspired puzzles with a magical floor that can be ripped out. Need to cross a gap? Use the floor next to you! Push boxes to open doors, manipulate signals, redirect laser by rotating mirrors and rewire entire floors full of electricity.",
