  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rip out the floor, rotate it and place it somewhere else!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/a85267eff2a1499bef5dc21e7b1504f5.poster.avif?t=1766443128\" width=800 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/a85267eff2a1499bef5dc21e7b1504f5.webm?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/a85267eff2a1499bef5dc21e7b1504f5.mp4?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sokowand </i>is a top-down retro puzzle game that fuses classic sokoban-inspired puzzles with a magical floor that can be ripped out. Need to cross a gap? Use the floor next to you. Need a button for a door? Steal it from the last room! But don't be too quick, some floors are more important than they seem to appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/b63d9745a620d9682f7f8b17ee2d9833.poster.avif?t=1766443128\" width=800 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/b63d9745a620d9682f7f8b17ee2d9833.webm?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/b63d9745a620d9682f7f8b17ee2d9833.mp4?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reassemble each of the 40+ rooms and build your way block by block - or rather floor by floor - to the goal. Push boxes to open doors, manipulate signals, redirect laser by rotating mirrors and rewire entire floors full of electricity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/e8916838a7b3eb31ef52d54aefc1adf3.poster.avif?t=1766443128\" width=800 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/e8916838a7b3eb31ef52d54aefc1adf3.webm?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/e8916838a7b3eb31ef52d54aefc1adf3.mp4?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sokowand</i> contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique twist on a classic puzzle genre</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45 Levels with an ever growing complexity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nostalgia inspired artstyle and soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hints for a more laid back experience </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/77902429c9cf66174be832fb85b15af6.poster.avif?t=1766443128\" width=800 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/77902429c9cf66174be832fb85b15af6.webm?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/77902429c9cf66174be832fb85b15af6.mp4?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
