rather floor by floor - to the goal. Push boxes to open doors, manipulate signals, redirect laser by rotating mirrors and rewire entire floors full of electricity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/e8916838a7b3eb31ef52d54aefc1adf3.poster.avif?t=1766443128\" width=800 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/e8916838a7b3eb31ef52d54aefc1adf3.webm?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/e8916838a7b3eb31ef52d54aefc1adf3.mp4?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sokowand</i> contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique twist on a classic puzzle genre</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45 Levels with an ever growing complexity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nostalgia inspired artstyle and soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hints for a more laid back experience </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/77902429c9cf66174be832fb85b15af6.poster.avif?t=1766443128\" width=800 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/77902429c9cf66174be832fb85b15af6.webm?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580100/extras/77902429c9cf66174be832fb85b15af6.mp4?t=1766443128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
